overview: This unique film takes you on a breathtaking journey to the most beautiful, graceful and wildest animals in the world. Experience how such clumsy animal babies discover the world. As different as all living organisms on our planet be - they all share the unfathomable 'miracle of life'. This documentation shows the fascinating wildlife shots in the most beautiful regions of the world - with sharp images thanks to high-definition movie technology.
title: Unser Leben das Wunder
